				\begin{document} $$ N_{S}(n) = \beta n^{2}+2~~n\ge{1};~~N_{S}(0) = 1   $$ \end{document}NS(n)=βn2+2n≥1;NS(0)=1

and 
11\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
